1. Check for the index where 'a' has occured the very first time.
2. If it is index 0, then check for the very first index at which s[i] != 'a', store this index in temp1 variable, then from temp1 check for the nearest occurence of 'a' and store in temp2 variable, and from temp1 till temp2 - 1, replace all the letters with their previous one (alphabetically).
